EN: In my opinion, he is a trustworthy person.

ZH: 以前，我们每年都会去海滩度假。
EN: In the past, we used to go on vacation to the beach every year.

ZH: 以此为例，我们能够更好地理解这个概念。
EN: Taking this as an example, we can better understand this concept.

